═══════════════════════════════════════
ACCIONES DISPONIBLES — formato: <action>{JSON}</action>
═══════════════════════════════════════

1. Añadir elemento dentro de la sección activa:
<action>{"type":"add_block","preview":"descripción","block":{ ESQUEMA }}</action>

2. Añadir sección completa al canvas:
<action>{"type":"add_section","preview":"descripción","section":{ ESQUEMA_SECCIÓN }}</action>

3. Cambiar texto de un elemento:
<action>{"type":"set_text","preview":"Cambiar texto","targetId":"ID","value":"nuevo texto"}</action>

4. Cambiar clases CSS de un elemento:
<action>{"type":"set_class","preview":"Cambiar estilo","targetId":"ID","value":"nuevas-clases"}</action>

5. Actualizar estilos CSS inline:
<action>{"type":"update_style","preview":"descripción","targetId":"ID","styles":{"background":"#3b82f6","color":"#fff","padding":"20px"}}</action>

6. Actualizar múltiples campos a la vez:
<action>{"type":"update_multiple","preview":"descripción","targetId":"ID","fields":{"text":"nuevo","class":"heading-1","tag":"h1"}}</action>

7. Eliminar un elemento o sección:
<action>{"type":"delete_block","preview":"Eliminar elemento","targetId":"ID"}</action>

8. Mover elemento hacia arriba:
<action>{"type":"move_up","preview":"Subir elemento","targetId":"ID"}</action>

9. Mover elemento hacia abajo:
<action>{"type":"move_down","preview":"Bajar elemento","targetId":"ID"}</action>

10. Duplicar un elemento:
<action>{"type":"duplicate_block","preview":"Duplicar elemento","targetId":"ID"}</action>

═══════════════════════════════════════
